\frac{1}{a(1+b)} + \frac{1}{b(1+c)} + \frac{1}{c(1+a)} \geq \frac{3}{ (abc)^{\frac{1}{3}}\big( 1+ (abc)^{\frac{1}{3}}\big) }
abc = k^3
\displaystyle a = \frac{kq}{p}, b = \frac{kr}{q}, c = \frac{kp}{r}
\displaystyle a(1+b) = \frac{kq}{p} \left(1+ \frac{kr}{q} \right) = \frac{k(q+kr)}{p}
k
(p+q+r)^2 \ge 3(pq+qr+rp)
\frac{p}{q+kr} +\frac{q}{r+kp} +\frac{r}{p+kq} \ge \frac{3}{1+k} 
\left(\frac{p}{q+kr} +\frac{q}{r+kp} +\frac{r}{p+kq} \right) ( p(q+kr) + q(r+kp) + r(p+kq)) \ge (p+q+r)^2
\frac{p}{q+kr} +\frac{q}{r+kp} +\frac{r}{p+kq} \ge \frac{(p+q+r)^2}{(1+k)(pq+qr+rp)} \ge \frac 3{1+k}
